    question: "How do you protect luxury finished basements with home theatres?",
    answer: "Luxury Vaughan basements with home theatres, wine cellars, and custom millwork require non-invasive waterproofing: interior crack injection using polyurethane foam (no excavation), strategic interior drainage systems hidden behind millwork, crystal drain systems for minimal floor disruption, and dehumidification systems for moisture control. We protect high-end finishes with floor coverings, dust barriers, and careful material handling. For exterior work, we use trenchless boring under interlock patios and restore landscaping to original condition. All work includes moisture testing and 25-year warranties to protect your investment."
