    question: "What warranty does DrySpace provide on Vaughan waterproofing?",
    answer: "DrySpace provides a 25-year transferable warranty on all Vaughan waterproofing projects covering materials and workmanship. The warranty includes: exterior membrane systems (25 years), weeping tile and drainage (25 years), crack injection repairs (25 years on polyurethane, 10 years on epoxy), sump pump installation (5 years on equipment), and foundation parging (10 years). The warranty is fully transferable to new homeowners (valuable for resale), backed by $5M liability insurance, and registered with Tarion as qualified renovation work. We've honored warranties across Vaughan since 1998 with a 99.2% success rate."
